    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a senior software engineer doing a code review.\n\nAnalyse this diff and respond in this EXACT format:\n\nSUMMARY:\n- [what the PR does in 2-3 bullet points]\n\nISSUES:\n- [list any bugs, security issues, or bad practices]\n- [write \"None found\" if the code is clean]\n\nSUGGESTED FIX:\n- [write the corrected code snippet for each issue found]\n- [write \"No fix needed\" if no issues were found]\n\nVERDICT: [write only LGTM or NEEDS CHANGES]\n\nRules:\n- VERDICT must always be the last line\n- If ISSUES contains anything other than \"None found\", VERDICT must be NEEDS CHANGES\n- If code is clean, VERDICT must be LGTM\n- Always provide a fix when there are issues, never leave SUGGESTED FIX empty\n\nDiff:\n{{ $('DIFF Parser').first().json.patchSummary }}",
        "options": {}
      },
